value: Thank you for the hard work recording the variety program.
It was a brand-new experience being able to work alongside those whom I would not normally meet.
Hey､ wassup! Kurou-chan~! Wanna head to the ending party after this?
Thank you very much for the invitation. However､ I have a few things to take care of today…
So how ‘bout we hang out a different day? I’ll be holding a party soon､ so drop by if you can!
Party… Umm､ do you have some basis for which you are celebrating…?
That’s not the sorta thing I wanna do it for! I wanna introduce you to a buncha people!
You can talk with tons of people… Ah
frame: it’s like one’a them tea parties you love!

value: Similar to a tea party… you say? In that case
frame: I hope you would do me the honor of participating.

value: You’ll come along with me? Then､I’ll be in your care there.
